# LTCG Calculator for Real Estate Investments in India

## Description

This C++ program calculates the Long-term Capital Gains Tax (LTCG) on real estate investments in India, as per two taxation schemes:
1. **Original LTCG Scheme** (with 20% tax and inflation adjustment).
2. **New LTCG Scheme (2024)** (with 12.5% tax and no inflation adjustment).

The program takes the year of selling the property as input, calculates the estimated selling price, and then computes the LTCG under both schemes. It also compares the taxes under both schemes to show which one results in a higher tax and by how much.

This program uses a CSV file (`Growth-price.csv`) that contains the yearly inflation rate and growth rate of property prices from 2001 to 2029.

### Code Author
The code for this program was generated by **ChatGPT** and not copied from any other source.

